SB134 Enrolled
1 Enrolled, An Act,
2
3
4 Relating to interstate warehouser tobacco tax; to amend
5 Sections 40-25-1, 40-25-4.1, 40-25-8, as last amended by Act
6 2025-448, 2025 Regular Session, 40-25-8.1, as last amended by
7 Act 2025-448, 2025 Regular Session, 40-25-16.1, 40-25-18, as
8 last amended by Act 2025-448, 2025 Regular Session, and
9 40-25-25, as last amended by Act 2025-448, 2025 Regular
10 Session, Code of Alabama 1975; to define an interstate
11 warehouser, to require an interstate warehouser permit issued
12 by the Department of Revenue; to add Section 40-25-15.1 to the
13 Code of Alabama 1975; to provide application and enforcement
14 provisions; to provide for penalties for noncompliance; and to
15 make nonsubstantive, technical revisions to update the
16 existing code language to current style.
17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
18 Section 1. Sections 40-25-1, 40-25-4.1, 40-25-8, as
19 last amended by Act 2025-448, 2025 Regular Session, 40-25-8.1,
20 as last amended by Act 2025-448, 2025 Regular Session,
21 40-25-16.1, 40-25-18, as last amended by Act 2025-448, 2025
22 Regular Session, and 40-25-25, as last amended by Act
23 2025-448, 2025 Regular Session, Code of Alabama 1975, are
