421 (h) Any unstamped tobacco product brought into the
422 state other than by an interstate warehouser, a manufacturer,
423 or an affiliate of a manufacturer for wholesale or retail sale
424 shall be deemed contraband and subject to confiscation and
425 applicable penalties.
426 (h) The department may adopt rules to implement and
427 administer this section.
